#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
#                                     DESCRIPTION
#----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------#
# sudo_open  :

# sudo_open takes a filename as an argument and allows you to select a 
# Cocoa or unix application with which to open your file using sudo.
